title: Light Coconut Cake
ingredients: ['250g plain flour', '300g caster sugar', '3 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon salt', '125ml vegetable oil', '7 egg yolks', '175ml water', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '1 teaspoon almond extract', '250ml egg whites', '1/2 teaspoon cream of tartar', '50g desiccated coconut']
